README of the MTDB (Mark Thomson's DataBase)
store multi-level hash structure in single level tied hash
and save that to a flat text database optionally with encryption

Contains code from MLDBM.pm written by Gurusamy Sarathy and Raphael Manfredi




- - - - - - - - - - - - - - 
INSTALLATION

You must install the following packages first:

  Data::Dumper
  Crypt::Blowfish
  Crypt::CBC  

From the MTDB source directory:

   perl Makefile.PL
   make install

is all that will be needed.


